description: This file defines the Todo data model class for a Flutter application, including fields, constructors, copyWith method, serialization to/from map for database storage, and annotations for immutability.

classes.name: Todo
classes.description: An immutable class representing a task in a to-do list with properties such as id, title, note, completion status, and timestamps.

methods.name: copyWith
methods.description: Creates a copy of the Todo object with specified fields replaced with new values.

methods.name: toMap
methods.description: Serializes the Todo object into a map for database storage.

methods.name: fromMap
methods.description: Creates a Todo object from a map, typically retrieved from the database.
